data.title: Pee Dee Family healthcare & pharmacy
data.meta_description: Genesis Healthcare provides affordable, high-quality healthcare in the Pee Dee area (Darlington, Olanta, Florence, & Lamar) as well as Walterboro, SC. We are a nonprofit, Federally Qualified Health Center dedicated to improving the health of our community through prevention, early intervention, rehabilitation, and education.
data.text:
Find Out

Who We Are

Genesis Healthcare is a nonprofit, Federally Qualified Health Center, with multiple locations in the Pee Dee area of South Carolina as well as Colleton county. We’re a community-focused healthcare provider, with a full range of medical services dedicated to improving the health of our community.

Learn More About Us

Explore

Our Services

At Genesis Healthcare we offer a wide variety of services to fit all your healthcare needs and concerns. Our many services are all housed at our main locations, allowing you to get all your healthcare needs and concerns for the entire family addressed in one stop. That is the Genesis way.

Explore Our Services

Learn How

We Can Help

Genesis isn’t your regular doctor’s or physician’s office. Like any other doctor’s office, we provide high quality healthcare services, but as a Community Health Center, we go beyond that. Genesis provides services to a multitude of insurance options, Medicare and Medicaid, and even to those who have no insurance.

Learn How We Can Help
